{
  "stem": "617.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We'd get-- like, we'd get a bread, and that bread would be divided into-- the bread was as big as a brick, and it was the shape of a brick.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was to be divided for five.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the daily ration of bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would get the black coffee in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at night, we'd get a soup.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was the food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A thick soup.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was some meat in it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But at first, we couldn't eat it, because it was smelly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But after a while, we could eat it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And some people used to get the bread, and they would eat it right away, and they'd have nothing all day.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But my sister and I, we always saved.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We always saved a piece for later, for other times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Came in handy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then we were there till August that year, 1944.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The name of the town was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] oh, I have to-- it was [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- like I said, it was in the-- we didn't see a town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All we could see is the forest and this empty space where we were staying.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, just-- because I remember, we were making up songs about it, you know, at night, after we came back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We would sit around and make up songs about the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], and I forget now what the words were like.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then in August-- and, like, I'm not sure of the date.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In August, all of a sudden we were taken to this lake, or water, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were walking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there, with little boats-- not big ones-- we were taken across.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We must have been walking a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were Latvians.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
